headline: Stablecoin Disruption: Time to Sell Your Visa Stock?
summary: Large retailers are trying to build stablecoins to circumvent Visa.  Investors should not panic and sell their Visa stock today.  This week, stablecoin legislation was approved by the United States Senate.
